Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:52.07,Main Dialog,Haruko,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, Reino!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:42.53,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Strejdo, strejdo...
